'''Club Deportivo Clan Juvenil''' is an [[Ecuador]]ian professional football club based in [[Sangolquí]]. They currently play in the [[Ecuadorian Serie A|Serie A]] after gaining promotion from the [[Ecuadorian Serie B|Serie B]].

