'''Chabab Ahly Bordj Bou Arréridj''' ({{lang-ar|'''شباب أهلي برج بوعريريج'''}}), known as '''CA Bord Bou Arréridj''' or simply '''CABBA''' for short, is an [[Algeria]]n [[Association football|football]] club based in [[Bordj Bou Arreridj]], founded in 1931. The club colours are yellow and black. Their home stadium, [[Stade 20 Août 1955 (Bordj Bou Arréridj)|Stade 20 Août 1955]], has a capacity of 15,000 spectators. The club is currently playing in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1]].

