The '''Macedonian Handball Cup''' ({{lang-mk|Ракометен куп на Македонија}}), is an elimination handball tournament held annually. It is the second most important national title in Macedonian handball after the [[Macedonian First League of Handball]]. Currently, [[RK Vardar]] holds the record for most titles won with 12.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rkvardar.com.mk/index.php?option=com_content&view=category&layout=blog&id=45&Itemid=74|title=Domasen Kup|work=RK Vardar|accessdate=2012-04-07|first=|last=}}</ref>
