{{Football club infobox | clubname = Lions| image = | fullname = The Lions FC| nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Stade Linité]], [[Seychelles]]| capacity = 10,000| chairman = | manager = Davis Khan| league = [[Seychelles League]]| season = 2014| position = 8th| }} '''The Lions FC''' is a [[Seychelles]]-based football club, currently playing in the [[Seychelles League]].<ref>https://int.soccerway.com/teams/seychelles/the-lions-fc/18467/matches/</ref>
The team is based in [[Cascade, Seychelles]] in [[Mahé, Seychelles|Mahe]] island but is made up of players from around the main island of Seychelles, Mahe.
==Stadium== Currently, the team plays at the 10,000 capacity [[Stade Linité]].
