{{infobox country at games | NPC = ISV | NPCname = | games = Paralympics | year = | flagcaption = [[Flag of the United States Virgin Islands]] | oldcode = | website = | location = | competitors = | sports = | flagbearer = | rank = | gold = 0 | silver = 0 | bronze = 0 | officials = | appearances = | app_begin_year = | app_end_year = | summerappearances = {{Team appearances list|team=Virgin Islands|competition=Summer Paralympics|begin_year=2012|end_year= }} | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
The '''[[United States Virgin Islands]]''' made its '''[[Paralympic Games]]''' début at the [[2012 Summer Paralympics]] in [[London]], sending a single athlete to compete in two [[para-equestrian]] events.<ref name="IPC">[http://www.paralympic.org/results/historical Virgin Islands at the Paralympics], [[International Paralympic Committee]]</ref>
The Virgin Islands has never taken part in the [[Winter Paralympic Games]], and no Virgin Islander athlete has ever won a Paralympic medal.<ref name="IPC" />
